screen_desc: The screenshot displays the full menu of "Bradman Pizza House," available from 4:30 PM to 9:40 PM. It includes various categories such as "Most Ordered," "Salads," "Kids Meal," "Desserts," "Sides," "Beverages," and several special deals. The menu highlights the number of items available in each category, with "Traditional Pizza" having the most options at 18, followed by "Gourmet Pizza" with 9, and "Chicken" with 6. Other categories include "Special Deals" for traditional and gourmet pizzas, as well as pasta, combos, and upgrades.
